OL,5,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's the day of reckoning for the
OL,7,     FB&Bers. Whose property will emerge
OL,8,     Ffrom the thud and blunder of
OL,9,     Fbitter recrimination as the best
OL,10,     Fvalue for money?
OL,11,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,12,     FGeorge tackles two Georgian
OL,13,     Fproperties: a Yorkshire town house
OL,14,     Fwith high ceilings and a heavy
OL,15,     Fchandelier, and a farmhouse in the
OL,16,     FPeak District that's a decorative
OL,17,     Fdisaster.
