OL,5,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,6,     FWe catch up with Cara and Ben in
OL,7,     FBishop's Stortford, where it's not
OL,8,     Fjust their family that's expanded.
OL,9,     FAnd after Tom and Kaitlyn's
OL,10,     Ffruitless search, did they venture
OL,11,     Finto Kent?
OL,12,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,13,     FPeter and Chard are building a new
OL,14,     Fhome. But he wants it to be round
OL,15,     Fwhile she says it should be
OL,16,     Fsquare. They're envisaging vastly
OL,17,     Fdifferent budgets. Oh, and it
OL,18,     Fneeds a plane workshop.
